Name: Ookibloks
About the game: OOKIBLOKS turns the action puzzle genre on its head with bright visuals, laughs, challenging game play, wacky characters and a super funky dance soundtrack. Ooki the monkey must take cute, furry revenge on a bunch of banana thieving crabs, but to do so he must : Force-feed a GIANT GHOST CAT until it FARTS ITSELF TO DEATH! Punch CRABS, FISH, MUSHROOMS AND PINK ICE CREAMS - in the FACE! Get help from a super cute flying ANGEL CAT! LAUNCH MISSILES from Ooki's little pink BUTT! All this and DAILY CHALLENGES that allow you to get more helping ITEMS from the OOKI BALLS vending machine! A 17 track MP3 soundtrack is also bundled for free!
